description:
Based on the grate job that PhiloHippus did in its Google Tahoma (unified font style) <http://userstyles.org/style/show/178> I created this addition to support the video.google.com domain.

ATTENTION: This style is an addition to PhiloHippus's Google Tahoma (unified font style) <http://userstyles.org/style/show/178>. They must be both installed or incorporated into one style.

@PhiloHippus, if you are reading this then you are more then welcome to go head and incorporate this style into your Google Tahoma (unified font style). They should go together.

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain(video.google.com)
{
  select
  {
    font-family: Tahoma !important;
    font-size: 8pt !important;
  }

  #playrightblock {width: 240px !important;}
  #playvideoblock {margin-right: 60px !important;}
}
